                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The tomb giant's claws carry the accursed power of their foul gods. A creature hit by the tomb giant's claw Strike becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1}.</p>"
